      <title>耶伦表示，更高的利率路径会增加收入的需求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-25/yellen-says-higher-path-for-rates-boosts-need-to-lift-revenue</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政部长珍妮特·耶伦表示，长期利率上升的前景使得遏制美国借贷需求变得更加困难，这凸显了在与共和党议员谈判中增加收入的重要性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-25/yellen-says-higher-path-for-rates-boosts-need-to-lift-revenue</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 25 May 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
